aptik (16.3.1) trusty; urgency=medium

  * Allow user to cancel apt cache backup and restore

  * Allow user to cancel PPA restore

  * Allow user to cancel theme backup and restore

  * Fixed: Check if --backup-dir exists in console mode
  
  * Fixed: --restore-ppa throws an error

  * Optimized commands --{list|backup|restore}-ppa to complete faster
  in console mode

  * Fixed: Unity desktop always displays window close button, even if
  disabled in code. Button action will be disabled where not required.

  * Added an embedded VTE terminal window for installing packages

  * Added option to backup and restore /etc/fstab and /etc/crypttab
  entries

  * Fixed an issue with --restore-themes command

 -- Tony George <tony.george.kol@gmail.com>  Sun, 27 Mar 2016 10:00:00 +0530
